government computer networks,

338
00:17:23,820 --> 00:17:27,340
civil servants have been barred
from using the internet.

339
00:17:27,580 --> 00:17:31,100
Andre Chichak visited a government
department recently

340
00:17:31,100 --> 00:17:33,900
to see how civil servants are coping.

341
00:17:35,980 --> 00:17:39,340
What has been a simple pleasure
for many government employees,

342
00:17:39,340 --> 00:17:41,780
