to over 100,000 computers

345
00:17:47,980 --> 00:17:51,260
used by public servants by June 2017.

346
00:17:51,620 --> 00:17:53,540
Big news for a small island.

347
00:17:53,540 --> 00:17:55,540
This announcement has,
of course, been met

348
00:17:55,540 --> 00:17:57,660
with a mixed response by the public

349
00:17:57,660 --> 00:18:00,260
and in particular,
government employees.

350
00:18:01,020 --> 00:18:03,940
I spoke to Mr Seow On Seow
of the IDA,

351
00:18:03,940 --> 00:18:06,300
the leading agency for this exercise,

352
00:18:06,300 --> 00:18:07,940
about this major decision.

353
